{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a025971c3f","title":"给邓颖超的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07f8896e8b","index":0,"year":1965,"month":9,"day":25,"articleId":"a025971c3f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"b30e52a28a","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1965年夏，毛泽东会见外宾后，邓颗超作为陪同人，曾问毛泽东是否作有新的诗词，并说“很久未读到主席的新作品，很希望能读到主席的新作品”。毛泽东以读谐语言所写的“你压追我写诗”，说的就是这件事。"},{"id":"58e7187076","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1965年写的《水调歌头·重上井冈山》和《念奴娇·鸟儿问答》。这两首词1976年在《诗刊》一月号公开发表时有所修改。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8457dfc2c7","type":"title","text":"给邓颖超的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"},{"id":"b30e52a28a","type":"paragraph","text":"邓大姐：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"},{"id":"58e7187076","type":"paragraph","text":"自从你压追我写诗叫以后，没有办法，只得从命，花了两夜未睡，写了两首词。改了几次，还未改好，现在送上请教。如有不安，请予痛改为盼！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"},{"id":"e29a224523","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"},{"id":"7b3363afcd","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"},{"id":"efcda51d70","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]邓颖超，当时任中共中央委员、全国人大常委会委员、全国妇联副主席。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f"}],"page":{"id":"b50e4dae20","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"a025971c3f","start":202,"end":202}}}},"__N_SSG":true}